In [755]:



    


wss= {}

for k in range(2, 21):
    kmeans_loop = KMeans(n_clusters=k,n_init=30,n_jobs=2,random_state=1000,verbose=0).fit(df_train_factors_cls) 
    clusters = kmeans_loop.labels_ 
    labels = kmeans_loop.predict(df_train_factors_cls) 
    print(silhouette_score(df_train_factors_cls, labels)) 
    wss[k] = kmeans_loop.inertia_
